external.description:
Are you looking for a unique take on the action RPG genre set in a dark fantasy world? Then you should check out the demo and Kickstarter for this upcoming game, Dungeons Deep! Crafted by Enraged Gamers, Dungeons Deep is a third person ARPG that seeks to create a gritty dark fantasy experience. It takes the usual style of the ARPG genre, and adding elements from other genres and games. From the level design, enemy design, and even the perspective the player has of the game. Unlike other ARPGs, Dungeons Deep doesn’t have the camera floating above the player character, but rather over their shoulder. This creates a more intimate feel, putting you in the midst of the action, facing down beasts of all shapes and sizes. These beasts can be found everywhere you go, as go crawling through this game’s dungeons. You will need to plan your movements and plans carefully, as hit boxes are precise and can decide your fate quick.
